    <item>
      <title>卡梅伦在国防开支问题上批评其他欧洲国家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/cameron-takes-aim-at-other-european-nations-on-defense-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国外交大臣戴维·卡梅伦将批评其他欧洲国家“不愿意”投资国防，同时他敦促西方民主国家在保护其利益和价值观方面“更加强硬、更加自信”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/cameron-takes-aim-at-other-european-nations-on-defense-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国政府将季节性工人签证计划延长至 2029 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/uk-government-extends-seasonal-worker-visa-program-to-2029</link>
      <description><![CDATA[允许英国农场季节性工人的签证途径已延长五年至 2029 年，让农业企业有时间投资自动化并摆脱对外国劳动力的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/uk-government-extends-seasonal-worker-visa-program-to-2029</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼制造规则威胁佐科维提升价值链</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/made-in-indonesia-rule-threatens-jokowi-s-move-up-value-chain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[4月中旬，外国商会的高管来到印度尼西亚一位部长的家中，呼吁取消新的进口规定，这表明私营部门对政府的贸易政策越来越感到震惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/made-in-indonesia-rule-threatens-jokowi-s-move-up-value-chain</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国的工厂过剩给世界敲响了警钟，但没有快速解决办法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/china-s-factory-glut-alarms-the-world-but-there-s-no-quick-fix</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对中国工厂产量的抱怨声不断高涨，但没有迹象表明北京已准备好采取可能对其脆弱的经济产生适得其反的补救措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/china-s-factory-glut-alarms-the-world-but-there-s-no-quick-fix</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院民主党阻止格林推翻议长约翰逊的企图</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/hardliner-greene-moves-to-force-vote-on-ousting-speaker-johnson</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院民主党与共和党联手阻止了强硬派推翻议长迈克·约翰逊的企图，这是一个罕见的跨党派联盟，旨在奖励这位共和党领导人帮助确保为乌克兰提供 610 亿美元的援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/hardliner-greene-moves-to-force-vote-on-ousting-speaker-johnson</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 21:22:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登警告称，如果以色列入侵拉法，他将扣留更多武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/biden-widens-rift-with-israel-in-move-that-paused-bomb-shipments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登表示，如果以色列继续对拉法发动地面入侵，他将停止向以色列运送更多进攻性武器，并谴责可能造成的平民生命损失是“错误的”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/biden-widens-rift-with-israel-in-move-that-paused-bomb-shipments</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 21:19:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞内加尔新总统宣布对渔业协议进行审计</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/senegal-s-new-president-announces-audit-of-fishing-agreements</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新当选总统巴西鲁·迪奥马耶·法耶表示，塞内加尔将审查与包括欧盟在内的合作伙伴签署的渔业协议和许可证，以确保它们得到优化以使该行业受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/senegal-s-new-president-announces-audit-of-fishing-agreements</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 21:13:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统为行李骚乱道歉，并寻求重置议程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/south-korea-s-president-tries-to-reset-his-agenda-with-rare-news-conference</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈就其妻子在可疑情况下收到名牌手袋一事首次道歉，凸显出他在议会选举惨败后为政府制定新方针所做的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/south-korea-s-president-tries-to-reset-his-agenda-with-rare-news-conference</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IBM 红帽因反白人男性偏见而被斯蒂芬·米勒的法律小组起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/stephen-miller-group-sues-ibm-s-red-hat-for-anti-white-male-bias</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前特朗普顾问斯蒂芬·米勒(Stephen Miller)的法律团队起诉IBM公司子公司红帽公司(Red Hat Inc.)，声称该公司的多元化目标导致一名前白人男性员工受到歧视性待遇并被解雇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/stephen-miller-group-sues-ibm-s-red-hat-for-anti-white-male-bias</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 20:32:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
